    <string name="about_app_description">My Wardrobe is a simple Android application for organizing clothes and creating outfits. Users can save clothing items, group them by category, and combine them into complete outfits.</string>
    <string name="about_app_how_to_use">How to use the app</string>
    <string name="about_app_steps">1. Register or log in to your account.\n2. Add clothing items with name, category, season, color, description, and image.\n3. View and manage your saved clothes.\n4. Create outfits by selecting a top, bottom, and shoes.\n5. View or delete your saved outfits.</string>
